HEADWORD: Woo
<hw>Woo</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p.
p.</pos> <conjf>Wooed</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Wooing</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[OE. <ets>wowen</ets>,
<ets>wo<?/en</ets>, AS. <ets>w<?/gian</ets>, fr. <ets>w<?/h</ets> bent,
crooked, bad; akin to OS. <ets>w⟦amac⟧h</ets> evil, Goth.
